## ğŸ’» TECHNICAL REQUIREMENTS

### **Codebase 1: Commercial Webpages**

**Technology Stack:**

- React (for interactive components)
- Tailwind CSS (custom vintage color palette)
- Framer Motion (for smooth, subtle animations)
- React Router (for navigation)
- Lucide React + Phosphor Icons

**Structure:**

```
/commercial
  /pages
    - LandingPage.jsx
    - PersonalBanking.jsx
    - BusinessBanking.jsx
    - AboutSecurity.jsx
    - LoginPage.jsx
  /components
    - Header.jsx
    - Footer.jsx
    - ServiceCard.jsx
    - Testimonial.jsx
    - etc...
  /assets
    /images
    /icons
```

### **Codebase 2: Online Banking Portal**

**Technology Stack:**

- React (complex state management)
- Tailwind CSS (consistent with commercial site)
- React Router (protected routes)
- Chart.js or Recharts (for analytics)
- React Hook Form (form handling)
- Framer Motion (transitions)

**Structure:**

```
/portal
  /pages
    - Dashboard.jsx
    - TransferMoney.jsx
    - Transactions.jsx
    - Accounts.jsx
    - Cards.jsx
    - BillPayments.jsx
    - Beneficiaries.jsx
    - Statements.jsx
    - Profile.jsx
    - Support.jsx
  /components
    - Sidebar.jsx
    - TopBar.jsx
    - AccountCard.jsx
    - TransactionList.jsx
    - etc...
```

**Security Features:**

- [ ] Authentication required for all portal pages
- [ ] Session timeout after inactivity
- [ ] Secure token storage
- [ ] HTTPS only
- [ ] Input sanitization

