## ğŸ¬ ANIMATION & EFFECTS (VINTAGE-APPROPRIATE)

**Animation Style:** Subtle, elegant, purposeful - think classic transitions not flashy effects

**Specific Animations:**

- [ ] **Fade-in on scroll** (gentle, slow)
- [ ] **Hover lift** on cards (2-3px, subtle shadow)
- [ ] **Number count-up** for statistics (smooth, not too fast)
- [ ] **Page transitions** (classic fade/slide)
- [ ] **Form field focus** (subtle glow in vintage colors)
- [ ] **Success checkmark** (draw animation, vintage style)
- [ ] **Loading spinner** (vintage clock or hourglass inspired)
- [ ] **Chart data** (gentle entry animations)

**Effects to AVOID:**

- âŒ Parallax effects (too modern)
- âŒ 3D transforms (doesnâ€™t fit vintage aesthetic)
- âŒ Aggressive bouncing
- âŒ Neon glows or vibrant gradients
- âŒ Particle effects

